The '''championship stage''' of the '''[[2013<U+2013>14 CONCACAF Champions League]]''' was played from March 10 to April 24, 2014. A total of eight teams competed in the championship stage.<ref name="regulations">{{cite web|url=http://www.concacaf.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/CCL1314-Regulations060313pdf.pdf|title=CONCACAF Champions League Regulations 2013/2014|publisher=CONCACAF.com}}</ref>

==Qualified teams==
The winners of each of the eight groups in the [[2013<U+2013>14 CONCACAF Champions League group stage|group stage]] qualified for the championship stage.

